Class DatasetGraphAltDefaultGraph

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.jena.sparql.core.DatasetGraphBase

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Closeable, DatasetGraph

    public class DatasetGraphAltDefaultGraph
extends DatasetGraphCollection
    DatasetGraph that switches the default graph to another graph. This different graph can be one of the underlying dataset or a completely unconnected graph. This wrapper should used with care at scale because it masks the query execution from storage, so generic query execution happens, not, for example, TDB quad execution.
